OL,3,CWhat is a supermajority and why do the
OL,4,CTories keep talking about it?
OL,6,FWith Labour leading significantly in
OL,7,Fthe polls, Prime Minister and Tory
OL,8,Fleader Rishi Sunak launched a 24-hour
OL,9,Fcountdown campaign on X to prevent
OL,10,Fwhat he calls a "Labour supermajority"
OL,11,Fled by Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,13,FThe term 'supermajority', usually
OL,14,Fassociated with US politics, refers to
OL,15,Fneeding more than a simple majority to
OL,16,Fwin a vote.
